Title: Hamiltonian Reduction of Non-Linear Waves
Authors: Marcos Alvarez
Comments: 15 pages, LaTeX
Report-no: SWAT-147
Journal-ref: Annals Phys. 261 (1997) 163-179
\\
  The Faddeev-Jackiw Hamiltonian Reduction approach to constrained dynamics is
applied to the collective coordinates analysis of non-linear waves, and
compared with the alternative procedure known as symplectic formalism.
